<TEXT>
<P>
The Los Angeles Police Department really showed its stuff in putting down the 
anti-abortion protesters on June 10. Yes, the police really showed that they 
can hand it out to those men, women and children by breaking an arm here and 
stepping on a head there. I'm not sure that it demonstrated the "right stuff," 
