ANGOLA -- REVOLTS; GUERRILLAS -- ANGOLA; SAVIMBI, JONAS; DOS SANTOS, JOSE 
EDUARDO; NATIONAL UNION FOR THE TOTAL INDEPENDENCE OF ANGOLA 
</P>
