<P>
DEMONSTRATIONS -- CHINA; DEMOCRACY; HUMAN RIGHTS -- CHINA; CHINA -- ARMED 
FORCES; CHINA -- MARTIAL LAW; BUSH, GEORGE; UNITED SATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS 
-- CHINA; MITCHELL, GEORGE J 
</P>
